data.description: Completed in 2021 this 4 bdrm + office/den, 3 bath, 3 car garage 2-Story in Gold Creek, is ready for its next owner. Upon home entry, you are engulfed in TONS of natural light, open concept living, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Spacious formal main level office/den, 1/2 guest bath, a sizable great room with lots of windows, huge kitchen open to main level, formal dining room with access to covered deck. Enjoy the large kitchen island and breakfast bar, stunning white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, pantry, and additional off kitchen butler pantry/pocket office space, or mud room. Upper level features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a laundry area. Full unfinished basement could provide up to 1150 Sq ft of additional living space upon future finishing. 3 car attached tandem garage w/ lots of additional storage. Superior wi-fi connectivity with a commercial-grade Ruckus network built in. The home was built with tons of high efficiency/energy star features. Enjoy low electric bills with the solar panels. This home screams beauty and space, nothing better, the complete package! Won’t last long!
